title: Malaria Outbreak - Kenya
content: WHO Africa reports confirmed malaria outbreak in western Kenya. Over 150 cases confirmed in Kisumu and surrounding areas. Response teams deployed.

title: Cholera Alert - Coastal Kenya
content: Ministry of Health confirms cholera cases in coastal region. Water sources being tested. Public advised to maintain hygiene.

title: Influenza Monitoring - Nairobi
content: Suspected increase in influenza cases in Nairobi. Surveillance ongoing. Public urged to seek medical care for symptoms.
